icized the Russian state including over plans to organize an international multi-sports event in September, weeks after the Paris Olympics close.Russian athletes who pass vetting to compete in Paris also will not take part in the opening ceremony parade of boats on the River Seine, the IOC decided this week.\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 1080, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 740, \"end\": 743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.931196267920489e-17, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 748, \"end\": 752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.999999971916623, \"rank\": 2.8083359854912844e-08, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 782, \"end\": 789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.9707054624325012, \"rank\": 0.0291047379775459, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 964, \"end\": 969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997384755148, \"rank\": 2.6152451706895007e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1041, \"end\": 1052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\